{
  "stem": "23942.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I understood all this in my mind, and I just-- I just functioned as a person.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Me, alone, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't need-- all I needed was a piece of bread to survive, a glass of milk or that, so I went to some of the goyim, and that's all.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every day, sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I missed them so much that you cannot even imagine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I dreamt terrible dreams.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was dreaming about my mother, and I was dreaming about my grandmother, and I was dreaming terrible dreams.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nightmares I had every night, and sometimes I was told I screamed, because when I got with other people, they told me I screamed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was-- I was always dreaming that the Nazis were coming after me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was-- I was somehow managed to get away from, outsmart them, just like I-- conscious, I knew I must do this, and subconscious.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- in other words, in the dreams, I had the same dreams what I was thinking during the day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The-- the nightmares was terrible in those days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I thought they will never leave me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was-- oh, this was another terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At night, I had terrible nightmares.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This lasted for many years.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Many years.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother, when I did dream, she didn't dream appear like I knew her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She was so veiled, and black veiled.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I-- I knew it was my mother, and yet she-- I couldn't see her face.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was so terrible when I did see her presence.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I knew it was her presence, but I couldn't recognize her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was so terrible, the dreams.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My lovely, beautiful mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She was veiled and black.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "What-- what it means, till today, I don't understand, but I-- but it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
